From 9d4c48fe8e38549ede960169f07b51c211c1d5fa Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: WalletWasabi contributors
Date: Thu, 21 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] wasabi: add p2p compact filter provider

Squashed local copy of the Wasabi P2P compact-filter PR.
It is stored this way so git apply sees only the final tree diff,
while the original PR commit subjects remain available below.

- Abstract the filters provider
- Connect to nodes that provide compact filters
- Add draft p2p filters provider
- Download Compact Filter Headers
- Download filter via P2P
- CR suggestions
- Refactoring (move code and renames)
- reorg
- Add some node seeds
- move up
- CompactFilterBehavior: Make TimeProvider required in `RequestTracker`
- CompactFilterBehavior: Simplify
- CompactFilterBehavior: GetNextRangeFiltersAsync -> GetNextFilterBatchAsync

---
